OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: Warehouse Reference Bill Of Material
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.FILTER_EXPRESSION: "( ( (w.id in (select ow.warehouse.id from OrganizationWarehouse ow where ow.warehouse.id = w.id and ow.organization.id = \'" + OB.getParameters().get('inpadOrgId') + "\' )) ) and ((w.swaWarehousetype in ('NO','VS')) and \'" + OB.getParameters().get('inpemSwaServiceorderId') + "\' = 'null') OR ((w.swaWarehousetype in ('SRV')) and \'" + OB.getParameters().get('inpemSwaServiceorderId') + "\' != 'null') ) and ((select count(PW.id) from swa_permissions_warehouse PW where PW.userContact.id = \'" + OB.getParameters().get('ssa_user_id') + "\' AND PW.permit=true)=0 or w.id IN (select PW.warehouse.id from swa_permissions_warehouse PW where PW.userContact.id = \'" + OB.getParameters().get('ssa_user_id') + "\' AND PW.permit = true))"
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.HQL: select w.id as id, w.name as name, w.searchKey||' - '||w.name as valuename from Warehouse w where @additional_filters@ and w.active=true

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: Orden por Concepto Reposición
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.FILTER_EXPRESSION: "e.ssaComboitemValue=\'ReposiciondecompraentreEmpresas\' and e.swaPercentReceived < 100 and e.ssaSpecialdoctype=\'SREPURCHASEORDER\' and e.documentStatus=\'SSA_CL\' and e.businessPartner.id = \'" +OB.getParameters().get('inpcBpartnerId') + "\'"

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: Warehouse Reference Orders All
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.FILTER_EXPRESSION: "( ((" + OB.isSalesTransaction() + " = true and w.id in (select ow.warehouse.id from OrganizationWarehouse ow where ow.warehouse.id = w.id and ow.organization.id = \'" + OB.getParameters().get('inpadOrgId') + "\' )) or (" + OB.isSalesTransaction() + " = false) ) and ( (w.swaWarehousetype in ('MI','CO') AND (\'" + OB.getParameters().get('inpemSsaComboitemValue') + "\' = 'consignacion')) OR (w.swaWarehousetype in ('NO','SA') AND (\'" + OB.getParameters().get('inpemSsaComboitemValue') + "\' <> 'consignacion') ) ) )" + " and ((select count(PW.id) from swa_permissions_warehouse PW where PW.userContact.id = \'" + OB.getParameters().get('ssa_user_id') + "\' AND PW.permit=true)=0 or w.id IN (select PW.warehouse.id from swa_permissions_warehouse PW where PW.userContact.id = \'" + OB.getParameters().get('ssa_user_id') + "\' AND PW.permit = true))"
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.HQL: select w.id as id, w.name as name, w.searchKey||' - '||w.name as valuename from Warehouse w where @additional_filters@ and w.active=true

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.HQL: select w.id as id, w.name as name, w.searchKey||' - '||w.name as valuename from Warehouse w where @additional_filters@ and w.active=true
